<p>Authorities in Crans-Montana, Switzerland, said fire safety inspections had not been carried out at the Le Constellation bar since 2019, after a New Year’s party fire there killed 40 people and injured more than 100 others. The disclosure has intensified scrutiny of local oversight and prompted public anger, as residents and officials grapple with questions about how the venue was monitored in the years leading up to the blaze. Bar owners issued their first public comments since the fire, saying they are overwhelmed with grief.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/O95UqiWOhT97DD2YASr5SfMgo2rA0LjOeVlCGkNkLTIz9k8ZqWdAjnnBm5MdPqokpr69iOP5Ga2hQ0zgEd5yvnJBoA45e-1rlPqGYhmgJdnYoEsETZ_NONyUOWTpjpStXW00tSIZROMZjm9X1fIuPrlTwIX2HPRXQmDUUqeJ6K-G' alt='Bouquets of flowers and candles were placed in tribute to the victims of the fire at Le Constellation bar in Crans-Montana (Switzerland) on January 6, 2026.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Teen victims: Several of those who died were teenagers, with some reported as young as 14, sharpening calls for accountability around venues hosting youth-heavy celebrations.</li><li>Town acknowledgement: The president of the town said municipal services had not inspected the bar since 2019, a statement that residents said left them feeling “anger” and “shame”.</li><li>Oversight accusations: Officials have faced growing accusations of lax oversight as details emerged about the multi-year gap in checks on the venue’s fire safety.</li><li>Owners’ nationality: The bar’s owners are French, according to reporting that also noted their grief as the community mourns.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Bar owners of Le Constellation: They said they are “overwhelmed with grief” in their first public comments since the fire. (<a href='http://www.euronews.com/2026/01/06/swiss-bar-owners-overwhelmed-with-grief-in-first-public-comments-since-40-killed-in-fire'>Euronews</a>)</li><li>Crans-Montana town leadership: Town officials acknowledged municipal services had not conducted safety inspections at the bar since 2019. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2026/01/07/after-the-crans-montana-tragedy-residents-express-anger-and-shame_6749158_4.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li><li>Local residents: Residents voiced “anger” and “shame” after learning inspections had lapsed for years. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2026/01/07/after-the-crans-montana-tragedy-residents-express-anger-and-shame_6749158_4.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/2026/01/06/swiss-bar-owners-overwhelmed-with-grief-in-first-public-comments-since-40-killed-in-fire'>Swiss bar owners &#x27;overwhelmed with grief&#x27; in first public comments since 40 killed in fire</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2026/01/07/after-the-crans-montana-tragedy-residents-express-anger-and-shame_6749158_4.html'>After tragedy at Swiss resort bar, residents express &#x27;anger&#x27; and &#x27;shame&#x27;</a> - lemonde.fr</li><li><a href='https://japantoday.com/category/world/swiss-bar-where-fatal-new-year%27s-fire-broke-out-had-last-safety-inspection-in-2019'>Fire safety inspections lapsed for years at Swiss bar where 40 died in New Year&#x27;s blaze</a> - japantoday.com</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/swiss-inferno-bar-owners-overwhelmed-with-grief'>Crans-Montana fire: French owners of Swiss bar ‘overwhelmed with grief’</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2026/01/06/world/europe/switzerland-le-constellation-fire-inspections.html'>Swiss Bar Hit by Deadly Fire Was Not Inspected for 6 Years, Authorities Say</a> - nytimes.com</li></ul>